  <div id='sd-about-middle'>
    <div id="sd-about-middle-01">
      <div class="sd-about-subtitle-03">TAKE YOUR SHOWDOWN EXPERIENCE FURTHER BY SIGNING UP TO RACENET!</div>
      <div class="sd-about-bodytext-03">Signing up gets you access to a whole range of exclusive features both in game and on the site!</div>
      <div id='sd-about-car'>
