        <div id='sd-about-bottomCopy'>
          <div class="sd-about-bodytext-04">KEEP YOUR EYE ON RACENET AS WE&#39;LL BE CONTINUING TO ADD NEW FEATURES IN THE COMING MONTHS!</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="sd-about-middle-02">
      <div id="sd-about-middle-02a">
        <img class="sd-about-floatright" src="./Content/Showdown/About/features.png" width="620" height="234" alt="Become a Showdown legend!" />
      </div>
      <div id='sd-about-arrows'>
        <div id='liveries'>
          <div class="sd-about-arrow"><h3>EXCLUSIVE LIVERIES</h3></div>
          <p class="sd-about-bodytext-03a">By signing up to RaceNet you’ll get access to an exclusive livery for the Ford Fiesta H.F.H.V. and qualify for an additional livery for Lafayette Eulogy and for the Lombardi 336LM. Keep checking back on RaceNet to find out how you can unlock these as we&#39;ll be announcing more details soon!</p>
        </div>
        <div id='events'>
          <div class="sd-about-arrow"><h3>RACENET EVENTS</h3></div>
          <p class="sd-about-bodytext-03b">Hitting the best times and scores takes skill but can you do this week on week? With RaceNet Events you’ll get a new challenge in DiRT Showdown every 7 days so set your best result and see how you stack up against the community back here on RaceNet.</p>
        </div>
        <div id='tour'>
          <div class="sd-about-arrow"><h3>TOUR, CHALLENGES &amp; MORE</h3></div>
          <p class="sd-about-bodytext-03c">Keep up to date with your DiRT Showdown tour progress, compare your best times and scores, track your challenge status with your friends or check in to see what you’ve got left to do in Joyride, it’s all here on RaceNet.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
