        <img src="./Content/Showdown/About/letloose.png" width="662" height="273" alt="LET LOOSE ON A TOUR OF MOTORISED MAYHEM" />
      </div>
      <div id='sd-about-letloosecopy'>
        <div class="sd-about-subtitle-02">DiRT Showdown comes with phenomenal graphical presentation, bone-jarring damage, and social online and split-screen multiplayer as standard. Welcome to DiRT Showdown - a new world of driving delirium.</div>
        <div id='sd-about-sections'>
          <div id='sd-about-first'>
            <div class="sd-about-bodytexttitle-02a">NO HOLDS BARRED RACING EVENTS</div>
            <p class="sd-about-bodytext-02a">Trade paint and use nitrous to blast past rivals in DiRT Showdown&#39;s racing modes. Courses are littered with obstacles, pinch points, multiple-routes and ramps to deliver adrenaline-fuelled racing across spectacular courses.</p>
          </div>
          <div id='sd-about-second'>
            <div class="sd-about-bodytexttitle-02b">EDGE OF CONTROL HOONIGAN EVENTS</div>
            <p class="sd-about-bodytext-02b">A new accessible handling system lets you go wild in free-roaming, freestyle stunt parks. Compounds flooded with obstacles play host to a range of new challenges, from performing trick runs to competitive stunt events, explorations, challenges and more.</p>
          </div>
          <div id='sd-about-third'>
            <div class="sd-about-bodytexttitle-02c">BONE CRUNCHING DEMOLITION DERBY EVENTS</div>
            <p class="sd-about-bodytext-02c">Crash, smash and bash your way through a range of demolition derby events, pushing our stunning damage engine to its spectacular limits.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
